\u003e\n    \u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003ctable class=\"module\" role=\"module\" data-type=\"text\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;\" data-muid=\"keQHYG1b1ztewxwhDtuCpS\" data-mc-module-version=\"2019-10-22\"\u003e\n      \u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\n        \u003ctd style=\"background-color:#ffffff; padding:10px 40px 20px 40px; line-height:22px; text-align:inherit;\" height=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv style=\"font-family: inherit; text-align: center\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003eThe Ingrid \u0026amp; Anders VIP club offers the following perks:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli style=\"text-align: inherit\"\u003eBirthday Gifts\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli style=\"text-align: inherit; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003eEarn Double Points\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli style=\"text-align: inherit; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003eSomething Else\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli style=\"text-align: inherit; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003eIn-Store Discounts\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli style=\"text-align: inherit; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif\"\u003eRedeem Points for Exclusive Items\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003ctable border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"module\" data-role=\"module-button\" data-type=\"button\" role=\"module\" style=\"table-layout:fixed\" wi